         <abstract>
            <p>
               A short theological treatise. It was probably translated from a Greek Vorlage. It is found in many manuscripts together with other Ethiopian theological and liturgical treatises, such as the Ethiopic 
               <title ref="LIT2461Testam"/> (as  <title ref="LIT2461Testam#Chapter22">Chapter 22</title>), <title ref="LIT1586Hayman"/>, and <title ref="LIT1544Gebrah"/>. 
               Sometimes it is bound together with the <title ref="LIT1960Mashaf"/>.</p>
            <p>Not to be confused with the text also known as <title ref="LIT3978Elmastoagya"/></p>
